The soapie announced that they will be holding auditions this coming weekend in Limpopo and encouraged fans to come along and try their luck.pic.twitter.com/q6SwaPYM1d Muvhango (@MuvhangoSA) April 4, 2017pic.twitter.com/q6SwaPYM1dAuditions will run from 9am till noon, with call backs on Sunday.The show has made headlines in the past after several audition scams claiming to be from Muvhango were shared on social media.One scam charged fans up to R300 for the chance to audition.